ẽ đi về đâu? Sự ngượng ngùng của họ đến bao giờ mới có thể lên đến đỉnh điểm? Cuối cùng Vee sẽ quyết định như thế nào?</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"204236","season":1,"vote_average":8.2,"vote_count":36},"modified":"2022-08-13T18:53:11.000Z","cast":["Anan Wong","Wanarat Ratsameerat","Ratchapat Worrasarn","Veerinsara Tangkitsuvanich","Kanidsorn Laiwrakoran","Nathadej Pititranun","Supitcha Limsommut","Thamrong Cunpisut","Saran Naksodsi","Wongrapee Krusong","Prat Itthichaicharoen","Natthapat Chanchaisombat","Thanakom Minthananan","Patsapon Jansuppakitkun","Ratchapong Anomakiti"],"director":["Lit Phadung Samajarn"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Anan Wong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Anan Wong","tmdb_id":2666128,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zXVxL9QcLma20Ibu4jxJsZB3L8x.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2666128"},{"name":"Wanarat Ratsameerat","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Wanarat Ratsameerat","tmdb_id":2595478,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jMh4iur4YzAJgqVzc3GqEHbuyL.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2595478"},{"name":"Ratchapat Worrasarn","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ratchapat Worrasarn","tmdb_id":2666131,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r9s0VrmJAIZnKBsqXkz7TqeHrpl.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2666131"},{"name":"Veerinsara Tangkitsuvanich","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Veerinsara Tangkitsuvanich","tmdb_id":2771757,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fWMCviCsg3P4lZcGgji94gLezpG.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2771757"},{"name":"Kanidsorn Laiwrakoran","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kanidsorn Laiwrakoran","tmdb_id":3670464,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/j0I76aES1HOsvimHM85l0vmKpxk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3670464"},{"name":"Nathadej Pititranun","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Nathadej Pititranun","tmdb_id":3670467,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ApttfmKbXoL7xEEWiQmCYxYDzKX.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.them